Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't merge this

IMO we'd better do:

1. add an assertion in https://github.com/openstack/glance/blob/master/glance/tests/functional/db/test_db_api.py#L31 to make sure 'wrapped' member is correct since new code in your change require it.

2. Adding function test cases to https://review.openstack.org/#/c/45822/2/glance/tests/functional/db/test_registry.py for checking the situation when 'use_tpool' option enabled.

Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't merge this

The code looks good. But as Zhi Yan said, could you please add a test case to cover the scenario of "use_tpool=True"? Thanks.

Patch Set 1:

Thanks for reviewing.

1. Done
2. I think db/test_registry.py does not test the rpc controller.
The v2/test_registry_api.py is the test file that tests the api/v2/rpc.py controller.
 And, although it's not a functional test, I am able to reproduce the bug with the test class that I have added.
